parameters:
\F[beni_trouble]Akane: "He's just a figurehead principal, often scolded by
the student council president. And yet, he looks at the
students with lecherous eyes. I don't think anything good
can come from talking to him..."
\F[beni_trouble]Akane: "Even so, you're going to talk to him?"
Yes
No
はい

Okajima: "Gufufufu... How unusual. A female student coming
to talk to me. I thought you all kept your distance."
\F[beni_trouble]Akane: "(So, he's aware of it...)"

\F[beni_smile]Akane: "I've been investigating if anything unusual has
happened at school recently... Principal, have you noticed
anything?"
Okajima: "Noticed anything? No... nothing!"
\F[beni_laugh]Akane: "Is that so? Then, excuse me."
Okajima: "Wait! I have something I want to ask you."
\F[beni_trouble]Akane: "What do you want to ask?"

Okajima: "It's about your senior in the detective club,
Suzukake-kun's career path. It's quite puzzling to me."

\F[beni_trouble]Akane: "Iruka-senpai's career path? That's a private
matter..."

Okajima: "I'm not asking out of curiosity. It's for proper
research!"
\FF[nako_trouble]Nadeshiko: "(What kind of research...? Suspicious...)"

\F[beni_trouble]Akane: "...Even if you ask, I don't know anything. He said
he was planning to go to the law faculty at university.
Don't you have his application or something?"

Okajima: "That's not it! I want to know if he has any
intention of returning here as a teacher! If he's going to
law school, it's different from what I was thinking!"

\F[beni_trouble]Akane: "(Iruka-senpai wanted to become a teacher!? I had no
idea...)"
\F[beni_trouble]Akane: "Iruka-senpai as a teacher?"

Okajima: "Such a talented individual. It would be troubling
if he doesn't return!"

\FF[nako_trouble]Nadeshiko: "Could it be... Principal, did you ask Iruka-
senpai to become a teacher?"
\F[beni_trouble]Akane: "Is that what this is about!?"

Okajima: "And yet he gives no reply! What a troublesome guy.
It seems like he's even avoiding me!"

\F[beni_trouble]Akane: "(Well... anyone would run away if approached by the
principal...)"

Okajima: "I'm not trying to make him my lover! I've never
touched him inappropriately or harassed him! So why does he
avoid me!?"

\FF[nako_trouble]Nadeshiko: "(No matter what he says, it sounds like he'd
make him his lover... and touch him inappropriately...)"
\F[beni_trouble]Akane: "(It must be his usual behavior...)"

Okajima: "Unbelievable! That's why I want you to find out
his true intentions!"
\F[beni_trouble]Akane: "(No... he definitely doesn't like it...)"

\FF[nako_true]Nadeshiko: "Understood. I'll convey to the principal that
you asked if he doesn't want to become a teacher."

\FF[nako_trouble]Nadeshiko: "(I have to say something or he'll keep pestering
us... Iruka-senpai is being targeted by the principal
too...)"

Okajima: "I'm counting on you! I'll be waiting for a
favorable response!"
\F[beni_trouble]Akane: "I think it's better not to expect too much..."

Okajima: "By the way, have you girls decided on your career
paths? You too... gufufufu! I think you have good
potential!"

\FF[nako_trouble]Nadeshiko: "(He's flipping through some documents... Are
they about us?)"
\F[beni_trouble]Akane: "Potential for what...?"

Okajima: "The potential to become my right hand and support
the academy as teachers! Always obeying me and spreading my
teachings to the students... a noble role indeed!"
\F[beni_shy]Akane: "Hahaha... That might be impossible."

Okajima: "No need for modesty! Along with Suzukake-kun, you
girls too..."

Okajima: "Gufufufu! Why not overthrow that cheeky student
council president and take control of the school now? How
about it? It's not a bad deal, right?"
\F[beni_trouble]Akane: "No, no... don't get carried away on your own..."

\FF[nako_trouble]Nadeshiko: "(Even Akane is totally put off... I, I
understand how she feels though)"

Okajima: "Please consider it! It will surely be for your own
good as well!"

\F[beni_trouble]Akane: "I, I definitely think that's not going to happen.
Excuse me..."
\FF[nako_true]Nadeshiko: "(Ah... she escaped...)"
A
いいえ

\F[beni_trouble]Akane: "(...I should stop. 'Don't poke the deity' as they
say.)"

Okajima: "Make sure to think about your future path!
Gufufu♪"
